@page user-doc-install svUnitTest installation

@section Sourceinstallation Source installation

@subsection Downloadthesources Download the sources

To download the sources, you can get the file on <a href='https://github.com/svalat/svUnitTest' target='_blank'>the download page</a>.

@subsection Buildandinstallthesources Build and install the sources

Now you may extract, build and install the sources :

@code
tar -xvzf svUnitTest-X.Y.Z.tar.gz
cd svUnitTest-X.Y.Z
mkdir build
cd build
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/yourprefix/
make
make install
@endcode

@subsection Changethecompiler Change the compiler

If you want to change the compiler, you can use :

@code
cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/yourprefix/ -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=icc
@endcode

